    <briefdescription>
<para>Used to construct an operator to apply a linear taper to either end. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Linear tapers are defined here as a time spanning a ramp running from 0 to 1. Data will be zeroed on each end of a 0 mark and a linear weight applied between 0 points and 1 points. Postive ramp slope on left and negative slope ramp on right. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
